languages.text: "Не стоит угрожать. Лучше подумай, чем выкупить свою свободу".
"Threats are unwise in your position. Better to think on what you have to barter for your freedom."
languages.original_text: "Не стоит угрожать. Лучше подумай, чем выкупить свою свободу".

traits.locale_text: "Threats are unwise in your position. I suggest you think what to buy your freedom with instead."
"Threats are unwise in your position. I suggest you think what to buy your freedom with instead."

languages.text: 「あなたの立場で脅迫するなど賢明ではない。そうではなく、何を使って自由を買うかを考えた方がいい」
languages.original_text: "Threats are unwise in your position. Better to think on what you have to barter for your freedom."

traits.locale_text: 「あなたの立場で脅迫するなど賢明ではない。そうではなく、何を使って自由を買うかを考えた方がいい」

languages.text: “站在你的立场，威胁我恐怕并不明智。你最好还是想想打算用什么来换取自由。”
languages.original_text: "Threats are unwise in your position. Better to think on what you have to barter for your freedom."

traits.locale_text: “站在你的立场，威胁我恐怕并不明智。我建议你好好想想打算用什么来换取自由。”

languages.text: «Las amenazas son imprudentes en tu posición. Te sugiero que pienses algo con qué comprar tu libertad en su lugar».
languages.original_text: "Threats are unwise in your position. Better to think on what you have to barter for your freedom."

traits.locale_text: «Las amenazas son imprudentes en su posición. Le sugiero que piense con qué comprar su libertad en su lugar».

languages.text: "Drohungen sind angesichts Eurer Lage unklug. Überlegt Euch lieber, was Ihr für Eure Freiheit bieten könnt."
languages.original_text: "Threats are unwise in your position. Better to think on what you have to barter for your freedom."

traits.locale_text: "Drohungen sind angesichts Eurer Lage unklug. Ihr solltet lieber darüber nachdenken, womit Ihr Eure Freiheit erkaufen wollt."

languages.text: « Vous n'êtes pas en position de me menacer. Vous feriez mieux de réfléchir à un moyen de négocier votre liberté. »
languages.original_text: "Threats are unwise in your position. Better to think on what you have to barter for your freedom."

traits.locale_text: « Vous n'êtes pas en position de me menacer. Je vous suggère plutôt de réfléchir à un moyen de racheter votre liberté. »

languages.text: "Bu hâldeyken tehdit savurman aptallık olur. En iyisi, özgürlüğüne karşılık bana neler sunabileceğini düşün."
languages.original_text: "Threats are unwise in your position. Better to think on what you have to barter for your freedom."

traits.locale_text: "Bu hâldeyken tehdit savurman aptallık olur. En iyisi özgürlüğünü kazanmak için nelerle pazarlık yapabileceğini düşün."
